    <h3 class="document__title">What will I need to drive in the EU after the UK leaves the EU?</h3>
    <p>From 28 March 2019, drivers from the UK will need extra documentation to drive in the EU and EEA. In the event that the UK leaves the EU without a deal, UK drivers may also need an international driving permit (IDP) to drive in the EU and EEA.</p>
